      "text": "is_dynamic?\nPR or Osc",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "center",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "active-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80, "y": 615, "width": 230, "height": 50,
      "strokeColor": "#0891b2", "backgroundColor": "#cffafe",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "active-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 90, "y": 618, "width": 210, "height": 45,
      "text": "[FROM PYTHON] Active Region Extraction\nRMS-based self-tuning\nthreshold = max(baseline+3, RMS/3)",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "sway-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 340, "y": 615, "width": 230, "height": 50,
      "strokeColor": "#dc2626", "backgroundColor": "#fee2e2",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "sway-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350, "y": 618, "width": 210, "height": 45,
      "text": "[FIXED] Dominant Axis Sway\ntheta = cumsum(gyro)*dt\nsway = max(theta) - min(theta)\n(was cumsum bug, now peak-to-peak)",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "decay-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80, "y": 685, "width": 230, "height": 60,
      "strokeColor": "#7e22ce", "backgroundColor": "#e9d5ff",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "decay-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 90, "y": 688, "width": 210, "height": 55,
      "text": "TKEO Energy-Burst Decay Onset\npsi_pos[n] = max(psi[n],0)\nthreshold = max(floor, q*max(psi))\nsnap to nearest local gmag peak",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "fft-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 340, "y": 685, "width": 230, "height": 60,
      "strokeColor": "#7e22ce", "backgroundColor": "#e9d5ff",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "fft-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350, "y": 688, "width": 210, "height": 55,
      "text": "Natural Frequency (FFT)\nSigned-axis Hann-windowed FFT\nDe-mean, band 0.5-25 Hz\nPad/truncate to 512 or 1024 bins",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "envelope-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80, "y": 765, "width": 230, "height": 55,
      "strokeColor": "#7e22ce", "backgroundColor": "#e9d5ff",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "envelope-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 90, "y": 768, "width": 210, "height": 50,
      "text": "Peak-Hold Envelope\nenv[0] = |g|[0]\nenv[n] = max(|g|[n], a*env[n-1])\na = exp(-2*pi*fc*dt), fc=2Hz",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "damping-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 340, "y": 765, "width": 230, "height": 80,
      "strokeColor": "#7e22ce", "backgroundColor": "#e9d5ff",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "damping-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 350, "y": 768, "width": 210, "height": 75,
      "text": "Bounded OLS Damping Ratio\nln(a_n) = ln(A0) - z*wn*t_n\nslope -> zeta = -m/(2*pi*fn)\nBounded: env > max(4*sigma, 0.03*peak)\nR2 > .90->high, > .70->med, else low",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "crossval-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80, "y": 840, "width": 490, "height": 55,
      "strokeColor": "#0891b2", "backgroundColor": "#cffafe",
      "strokeWidth": 1.5, "roundness": {"type": 3},
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "crossval-text",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 90, "y": 843, "width": 470, "height": 50,
      "text": "[FROM PYTHON] Frequency Cross-Validation\nCompute ZC freq (zero-crossing periods) and PK freq (peak-to-peak periods)\nWarn if |FFT - ZC|/FFT > 20%  ->  possible signal quality issue",
      "fontSize": 10, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeStyle": "solid", "opacity": 100
    },
    {
      "id": "params-box",
      "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 80, "y": 915, "width": 230, "height": 75,
